  • This tee will have you feeling like you have wings! 

    Dandelion Flying Mushroom Seed Tee is the perfect shirt for anyone who loves nature, fantasy and adventure. This tee features a whimsical design of a dandelion with mushroom-shaped seeds flying in the wind. The soft and breathable fabric will keep you comfortable all day long. Whether you're exploring the woods, reading a fairy tale or just relaxing at home, you'll love wearing this magical tee.

    Available in 10 colors and 7 different sizes,     measurements are shown below. We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.


    Size (inches) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning
